Getting Started React JS 1
--

Prerequiste
---
  - HTML, CSS, JS
  - Install node.js (include npm/yarn)

* Step
---
- Makesure node JS version
  $ node -v
  $ npm -v
- create-react-app (npm version 5.2+)

Start
---
1. Create project
  $ npx create-react-app react-js
  $ npm init react-app react-js
  $ yarn create react-app react-js
2. Open Project
  $ cd react-js
3. Remove default git 
  $ rm -rf .git
4. Running
  $ npm start/npm run start


Info 
--
  dependencies -> package dibutuhkan untuk menjalankan project
  devDependencies -> package yang dibutuhkan untuk environment development


Membuat component state
-- 

